	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  And the administrations concerned 
and hed let you know
	     
	     Q	  And did he
	     
	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  Yes  Absolutely  What did he say 
this morning
	     
	     Q	  It had to be dragged out of you here yesterday
	     
	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  It didnt have to be dragged out of 
