	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  I think at this point theres no 
changes in the schedule at all  I dont know that they discussed the 
timing like that
	     
	     Q	  Do you believe that youre closer or getting closer 
this week than you were last week
	     
	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  Again I believe that were going 
to pass a jobs package  The President is prepared to make 
adjustments in order to get that to happen  I dont know where the 
votes are on cloture at this particular time  I dont know whats 
going to happen until we have a vote  But the President believes 
deeply in this jobs package and wants to get it done
	     
	     Q	  Has there been any indication that this situation 
has changed
	     
	     MR STEPHANOPOULOS  Were going to continue to work on 
it  Well know when the votes are taken
	     
	     Q	  George last week you said that there are  or 
various people in the administration were saying that you couldnt go 
